537
00:25:53,620 --> 00:25:54,460
Jom pergi.

538
00:25:54,620 --> 00:25:55,460
Awak pergi beli sendiri.

539
00:25:57,580 --> 00:25:58,540
Saya akan pergi ke dinding.

540
00:25:58,700 --> 00:25:59,820
(Shuozhou)

541
